loat_shares":316589.0,"held_pct_insiders":0.84288,"held_pct_institutions":0.0,"fifty_two_week_high":250.0,"fifty_two_week_low":138.65,"fifty_day_average":203.016,"two_hundred_day_avg":218.51025,"recommendation":"none","all_time_high":388.5,"all_time_low":71.0,"long_business_summary":"Vruddhi Engineering Works Limited designs, engineers, and supplies rebar couplers to real estate, construction, and infrastructure industries in India. The company offers bolted, cold forged, precast, parallel roll threaded, taper threaded, and hydraulic crimping couplers, as well as terminator rebar, groutfit, and reducer couplers. It also provides Vruddhi Sonic Tube (VST), a product designed to ensure quality in deep foundation testing, such as diaphragm walls, drilled shafts, and bored piles; and Vruddhi Wall Cone Tie (VCT), a construction product used to secure formwork panels. In addition, the company offers construction materials, including TMT Bars, MS Structures, and MS plates and pipes; rebar threading, rebar roller threading, rebar cold forging, bandsaw cutting, and proofloading machines; and machine spares, such as chasers, cutting blade, machine dia and punch, protection caps, and rollers. Further, it provides parallel roll threading, rebar cold forging and threading, mobile van, and on-site machine work services; and trading in threading machines and spares. The company was formerly known as Vruddhi Steel Limited and changed its name to Vruddhi Engineering Works Limited in April 2023. Vruddhi Engineering Works Limited was incorporated in 2020 and is headquartered in Mumbai, India."}}